      "text": [
        "2166 - وَ كَانَ رَسُولُ اَللَّهِ صَلَّى اَللَّهُ عَلَيْهِ وَ آلِهِ : يَسْتَهْدِي مَاءَ زَمْزَمَ وَ هُوَ بِالْمَدِينَةِ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.2166 - The Messenger of Allah (swt), peace and blessings be upon him and his family, used to request Zamzam water while he was in Madinah."
        ]
      }
